Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.71,0:00:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 丫头\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hey, kiddo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.71,0:00:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,猜你是在琢磨老爸的大炖锅里在做什么美味吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}Guess you're wondering what old Dad is up to with the big stew pot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.86,0:00:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs26\an8}来给厨师送吻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.69,0:00:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,再猜\N{\fnArial\fs18}Guess again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.58,0:00:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria 老爸大半夜被一个想法给弄醒了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Daria, I woke up in the middle of the night with a hankering.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.03,0:01:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我忽然就想起来以前军校...\N{\fnArial\fs18}I suddenly remembered the old kitchen sink stew
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.08,0:01:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,他们总给我们做的槽炖大菜了\N{\fnArial\fs18}they used to serve us at the military academy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.43,0:01:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,知道为啥叫槽炖大菜不?\N{\fnArial\fs18}You know why they called it that?
