Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.08,0:01:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他们把食材全都扔到厨房水槽里炖\N{\fnArial\fs18}Because they put in everything but the kitchen sink.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.36,0:01:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他们把食材全都扔到厨房水槽里炖\N{\fnArial\fs18}Because they put in everything but the kitchen sink!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.18,0:01:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,看看哈 老汤 干胡椒 牛至叶 干辣椒\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hmm, let's see... soup stock, peppercorns, oregano, chilies...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.80,0:01:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你爸这是怎...\N{\fnArial\fs18}Why is your father...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.77,0:01:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,别问我\N{\fnArial\fs18}Don't ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.95,0:01:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,看东西呢是吧?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Reading something?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.20,0:01:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.51,0:01:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,能问问是啥不?\N{\fnArial\fs18}May I ask what it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.56,0:01:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,书 老师的任务\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's a book. For school.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.71,0:01:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,讲科幻小说存在的意义远远不止娱乐大众\N{\fnArial\fs18}About how fiction should do more than just entertain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.74,0:01:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,听起来蛮有趣的\N{\fnArial\fs18}That sounds interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.52,0:01:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 一个作家出书阐述作家应该如何写书\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yeah. A writer writing a book about how writers should write books.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.64,0:01:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定会是一本畅销书\N{\fnArial\fs18}Must have been a huge seller.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.13,0:01:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那... 学校里有没有发生别的什么事?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Well... anything else going on in school?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.97,0:01:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我想想 这礼拜没人跟我搭话\N{\fnArial\fs18}Let's see... nobody talked to me again this week,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.93,0:01:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,周末也没被邀请参加任何派对\N{\fnArial\fs18}I wasn't invited to any parties for the weekend,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.32,0:01:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,另外我嘴边好像长了几颗巨疼无比的疱疹\N{\fnArial\fs18}and I think I'm getting one of those really painful cold sores.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.42,0:01:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,所以总结一下 又是超赞的一周\N{\fnArial\fs18}So all in all, another great week.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.68,0:01:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria啊\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, Daria...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.91,0:02:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Helen Helen 911电话号码是多少来着?!\N{\fnArial\fs18}Helen! Helen! What's the number for 911?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.23,0:02:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria 你看事情一定要这么消极的眼光吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Daria, do you have to look at everything in such a negative light?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.80,0:02:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那您意思是让我用自然界的刺眼日光吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Could you possibly be referring to the harsh light of reality?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.91,0:02:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Tiffany说会有一股冷锋来袭\N{\fnArial\fs18}Tiffany says a cold front is coming through.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.77,0:02:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你们谁看见我那件超萌的粉红绒绒毛衣了吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Has anyone seen my really cute fuzzy pink sweater?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.48,0:02:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我找不到了 可不可以再买一件 谢啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}And if I can't find it can I buy another one? Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.99,0:02:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- Daria - 别劳神了\N{\fnArial\fs18}- Daria... - Don't bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.04,0:02:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我的舌头 老天啊 都发黑了 Helen呐\N{\fnArial\fs18}My tongue! Dear God, it's black! Helen!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.25,0:02:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这就来啦 Jake\N{\fnArial\fs18}Be right there, Jake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.90,0:02:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,因此加德纳想要告诉我们的是 科幻小说的作者...\N{\fnArial\fs18}So, what Gardner is telling us is that the writer of fiction
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.06,0:02:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,应当不仅仅把职责限于给读者讲述一个故事\N{\fnArial\fs18}has a duty that goes beyond the mere telling of a story.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.73,0:02:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的职责应该是 在讲故事的同时 让读者们能够...\N{\fnArial\fs18}His or her job is to tell a story in such a way as to leave the reader...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.80,0:02:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,怎样呢 Kevin?\N{\fnArial\fs18}what, Kevin?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.95,0:02:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,呼唤更多的激烈肉搏场景?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Screaming for more full-contact martial arts excitement?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.93,0:02:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Daria?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.86,0:02:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我想加德纳先生是希望作者能够...\N{\fnArial\fs18}I believe Mr. Gardner feels it's the writer's duty
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.83,0:02:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,引导读者能够更加向善而为\N{\fnArial\fs18}to steer the reader toward more conscientious behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.88,0:02:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不管这会使故事变得多么无趣\N{\fnArial\fs18}No matter how dull that makes the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.50,0:02:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,非常好 Daria\N{\fnArial\fs18}Very good, Daria.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.23,0:02:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 把这件事牢记于心 我希望大家每人...\N{\fnArial\fs18}Now, keeping that in mind, I want you each
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.65,0:03:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,选择从面前的书单中选择一本书 就其道德导向写一篇报告\N{\fnArial\fs18}to select a book from the list in front of you for a report on its moral intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.99,0:03:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 Kevin?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yes, Kevin?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.75,0:03:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,住在玻璃房里的人不应该乱扔石头\N{\fnArial\fs18}People who live in glass houses shouldn't throw stones.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.64,0:03:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我抢到一个 宝贝 抢到一个\N{\fnArial\fs18}I got one, babe. I got one!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.94,0:03:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰下\N{\fnArial\fs18}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.10,0:03:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 Daria\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yes, Daria?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.20,0:03:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,您给的书单... 我已经全读完了\N{\fnArial\fs18}This list of books... I've read all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.76,0:03:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.27,0:03:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那你想不想再多读一本呢?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Um, would you like to pick another book to read then?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.95,0:03:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- 可以吧 - 等等 脑暴时间\N{\fnArial\fs18}- I guess. - Wait, brainstorm!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.85,0:03:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,与其再读一个以道德引导为目的的故事\N{\fnArial\fs18}Instead of trying to read a story for its moral dimensions,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.14,0:03:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你何不亲自尝试写一个这样的故事?\N{\fnArial\fs18}what if you wrote a story with moral dimensions?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.18,0:03:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,独家课业任务 只派给你哦\N{\fnArial\fs18}A special assignment, Daria just for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.89,0:03:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道 写什么人好呢?\N{\fnArial\fs18}I don't know. Who would I write about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.19,0:03:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,写他们什么呢?\N{\fnArial\fs18}What would they do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.21,0:03:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这个... 不如你把在现实生活中认识的人集结到故事中\N{\fnArial\fs18}Well, why don't you write a story taking people you know in real life
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.88,0:03:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,再把他们转换成虚构角色\N{\fnArial\fs18}and turning them into fictional characters?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.98,0:03:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我在想会有人看出差别吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}I wonder if anyone would notice the difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.66,0:03:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你那故事构思怎样了?\N{\fnArial\fs18}So, how's the story coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.19,0:03:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我说话不会打扰到你吧?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Or does it disturb you if I talk while you're writing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.49,0:03:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我要是真有动笔 你才会打扰到我\N{\fnArial\fs18}It would disturb me if I were actually doing any writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.51,0:03:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这有何难?\N{\fnArial\fs18}What's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.53,0:03:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,把你认识的人写进去 随心所欲安排他们做的事\N{\fnArial\fs18}Take people you know and have them do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.17,0:03:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,要是我 就让他们满地匍匐 匍匐\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'd make them crawl, I tell you. Crawl!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.99,0:03:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,放松 虎妞\N{\fnArial\fs18}Easy, tiger.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.85,0:04:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底要写谁?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Who you going to write about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.34,0:04:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,没思路啊\N{\fnArial\fs18}I haven't a clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.24,0:04:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,写Kevin和Brittany怎么样?\N{\fnArial\fs18}How about Kevin and Brittany?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.15,0:04:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以从他们的激萌恋爱一路写到浪漫童话婚礼\N{\fnArial\fs18}You could write a thrilling romance leading up to their storybook wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.11,0:04:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,再激萌浪漫 也得先有个开始才行啊\N{\fnArial\fs18}You need to start wearing a hat when you go out in the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.61,0:04:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我去 要不我在这俩货过不下去要上吊时掺和一脚?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Boy, would I like to be there when those two tie the noose.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.75,0:04:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那么你 Kevin\N{\fnArial\fs18}And do you, Kevin,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.41,0:04:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是否愿意娶这位美貌的女子做你的合法妻子?\N{\fnArial\fs18}take this pulchritudinous woman to be your lawfully wedded wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.09,0:04:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Kevin\N{\fnArial\fs18}Kevin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.41,0:04:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我... 您说啥?\N{\fnArial\fs18}I, uh... what did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.16,0:04:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我说 你 Kevin 是否愿意承担法律责任\N{\fnArial\fs18}I said, do you, Kevin, assume legal responsibility
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.45,0:04:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,娶你身旁这位成熟大发的怪女人为妻?\N{\fnArial\fs18}for this overripe specimen of femalehood standing next to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.44,0:04:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,穿白衣服这位 孩子\N{\fnArial\fs18}The one in white, son!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.95,0:04:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Kevin Kevin\N{\fnArial\fs18}Kevin! Kevin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.04,0:04:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,说啊\N{\fnArial\fs18}Well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.89,0:04:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,回答人家呀 Kevvy\N{\fnArial\fs18}Answer him, Kevvy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.10,0:04:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Kevin\N{\fnArial\fs18}Kevin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.98,0:04:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Jane\N{\fnArial\fs18}Jane!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.32,0:05:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Brittany\N{\fnArial\fs18}Ah... Brittany.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.45,0:05:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,请接受我对你不幸遭遇的深切慰问\N{\fnArial\fs18}Please accept my condolences on the unfortunate way,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.30,0:05:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,在你人生最重要的日子里 他跑了\N{\fnArial\fs18}the biggest day of your life, has turned out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.11,0:05:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,爽\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.69,0:05:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria? Daria 写写他们的婚礼嘛\N{\fnArial\fs18}Daria? Daria! What about their wedding?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.02,0:05:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,想想就觉得会很有意思\N{\fnArial\fs18}Wouldn't that be funny to write about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.97,0:05:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,什么? 算了... 我不觉得\N{\fnArial\fs18}What? Uh... no. I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.23,0:05:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧...\N{\fnArial\fs18}Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.59,0:05:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我意思是... 要是写结成配偶仪式的题材\N{\fnArial\fs18}I mean, if I were going to write about mating rituals,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.40,0:05:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那我还不如写几百年前的那种\N{\fnArial\fs18}I think I'd go back a couple hundred years,
