Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.86,0:05:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈说每次来拜访你 他就特别特别紧张\N{\fnArial\fs18}Mother said he appeared most anxious to call upon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.59,0:05:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,真想不通是为什么 Lane先生的脾气 看法...\N{\fnArial\fs18}I cannot imagine what for. Mr. Lane's temperament, outlook,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.29,0:05:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,气质和他怪异的风度更容易让人产生困惑\N{\fnArial\fs18}indeed, his very manners are such as to arouse bemusement
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.95,0:05:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,胜过了对他的热心所生发出的喜爱\N{\fnArial\fs18}rather than endearment in the object of his attentions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.46,0:05:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他太古怪\N{\fnArial\fs18}He's flaky.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.52,0:05:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然确实有些古怪 可终有一天 整个德文天郡都会是他的\N{\fnArial\fs18}Flaky though he may be, one day, all of Devonheavenshire will be his...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.23,0:06:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,真不知道到时谁能那么幸运成为Lane太太呢\N{\fnArial\fs18}his to share with whosoever is lucky enough to become Lady Lane.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.62,0:06:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,乖妹妹呀 我真心希望不管谁成为Lane太太\N{\fnArial\fs18}Dear sister, I would hope that whoever does become lady lane
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.20,0:06:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,都只是出于对Lane先生的爱慕 而不是惦记他的房\N{\fnArial\fs18}does so out of regard for Mr. Lane and not for his estate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.51,0:06:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,惦记车行吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}What about his car?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.56,0:06:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,快看呀 Lane先生骑马过来了呢\N{\fnArial\fs18}But look! Here approaches Mr. Lane himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.10,0:06:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,跟着他妹妹的追求者 Moreno先生\N{\fnArial\fs18}along with his sister's admirer, Mr. Moreno.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.29,0:06:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好 Morgendorffer小姐 Quinn小姐\N{\fnArial\fs18}Good morning, Miss Morgendorffer, Miss Quinn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.97,0:06:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,祝福两位佳人今日愉悦\N{\fnArial\fs18}I pray the day finds you well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.29,0:06:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,也向两位祝好 先生们\N{\fnArial\fs18}And a good morning to you, sirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.04,0:06:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 今早注定会是一个明媚的早晨\N{\fnArial\fs18}Indeed, it promises to be a glorious morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.40,0:06:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,即使最坚硬的心也会为之融化\N{\fnArial\fs18}and one to gladden the stoniest of hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.77,0:06:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,诚愿如此 固然 世间荣华富贵皆为美\N{\fnArial\fs18}Let us hope so, indeed, for nothing so recommends this world
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.27,0:06:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,但最怡然仍是度过心旷神怡的每一天\N{\fnArial\fs18}as the promise with which it offers up each gentle day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.37,0:06:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,请问 在这晨露熹微的清早\N{\fnArial\fs18}And, pray, upon this dewy morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.61,0:06:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,两位是有什么差事要远驾至此?\N{\fnArial\fs18}what errand is it that finds you guys abroad?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.68,0:06:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,没有什么差事\N{\fnArial\fs18}Errand we have none.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.33,0:06:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不过非常幸运 我们今天外出运动\N{\fnArial\fs18}But with any luck, we shall have sport.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.89,0:06:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在等狩猎俱乐部的其他成员\N{\fnArial\fs18}We await the other members of our hunting party,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.27,0:06:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,相信迎面过来的就是他们了\N{\fnArial\fs18}and I believe I glimpse them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.89,0:07:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好\N{\fnArial\fs18}Good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.67,0:07:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Quinn小姐 需要为你寻一处饮茶栖息处吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Miss Quinn, may I get you a bracing spot of tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.68,0:07:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,需要防滑粉吗? 今天雾大容易手滑\N{\fnArial\fs18}Do you need a powder, to cure the vapors?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.24,0:07:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我来为你的钢琴调音吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'll tune your pianoforte.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.54,0:07:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Quinn呀 你的追求者好多 全都因为你是如此的完美动人\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, Quinn, your suitors are so numerous because you are so fair and good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.33,0:07:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐呀\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.82,0:07:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,凭你的智慧和判断力 一定可以嫁一个殷实又明智的郎君\N{\fnArial\fs18}your wit and judgment assure that you will marry not only well, but wisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.10,0:07:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,她说"嫁"了吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Did she say "marry"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.67,0:07:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.12,0:07:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.14,0:07:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我写故事烂透了\N{\fnArial\fs18}I really suck at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.69,0:07:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 绝对不行\N{\fnArial\fs18}No. No, absolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.03,0:07:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,没有商量的余地\N{\fnArial\fs18}That is unacceptable.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.11,0:07:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊 你爸这又是在煮什么呢?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, my God, what has your father done now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.89,0:07:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Jake\N{\fnArial\fs18}Jake!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.74,0:07:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Daria?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.45,0:07:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你哪里不舒服吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.95,0:07:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不舒服? 没呀\N{\fnArial\fs18}Wrong? Uh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.01,0:07:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我在琢磨学校里老师留的一个作业呢\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'm thinking about an assignment I got in school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.34,0:07:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,妈能帮你点啥吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Anything I can help with?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.17,0:07:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,算了\N{\fnArial\fs18}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.79,0:08:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我要写一个故事 把身边的人换成虚构角色写进去\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'm supposed to write a story using people I know as fictional characters.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.79,0:08:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是嘛 听起来棒极了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Really? That sounds fascinating.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.89,0:08:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,别急啊 我写出来的东西就烂透了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Not so far. Everything I write comes out bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.20,0:08:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,建立不起故事\N{\fnArial\fs18}I have no story.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.65,0:08:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我肯定...\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, I'm sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.90,0:08:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,稍等一下 Daria\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hang on a second, Daria.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.94,0:08:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,喂? 你那不叫买方还价 赤裸裸的侮辱好吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hellooo. No, that's not a counteroffer, it's an insult.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.85,0:08:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,明天上班以后我会找你谈的\N{\fnArial\fs18}I will talk to you tomorrow during office hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.43,0:08:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,再见\N{\fnArial\fs18}Good-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.10,0:08:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好啦 说说其他孩子都写了什么咯\N{\fnArial\fs18}Okay, now, what are the other students writing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.46,0:08:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不用写\N{\fnArial\fs18}They're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.53,0:08:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这是老师单独给我派的额外作业\N{\fnArial\fs18}This is an extra assignment just for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.38,0:08:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,惩罚我如此聪明\N{\fnArial\fs18}A punishment for being smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.38,0:08:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好啦好啦 Daria\N{\fnArial\fs18}Now, come on, Daria,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.72,0:08:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈相信只要你用心 一定可以写出好故事的\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'm sure you'll do a great job if you just put your mind to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.51,0:08:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你这话错到姥姥家了\N{\fnArial\fs18}You are very, very wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.40,0:08:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,一定可以的 你只管...\N{\fnArial\fs18}Sure you will. All you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.21,0:08:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,喂?! 明天 上班时间谈\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yes?! Tomorrow! During office hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.18,0:08:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你只管甩掉一身的酷细胞 放开手去写好了\N{\fnArial\fs18}All you have to do is get off your toches and do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.34,0:08:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,人家Quinn一遇到挑战...\N{\fnArial\fs18}When Quinn has a challenge...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.07,0:08:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Quinn?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Quinn?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.87,0:08:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,她遇到的挑战仅限于穿什么样的鞋子搭配男伴的眼睛颜色吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}All her challenges involve coordinating her shoes with the color of her date's eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.65,0:08:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria 我要说的是...\N{\fnArial\fs18}Daria, what I mean is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.71,0:09:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你干嘛要拿Quinn摆出来说事?\N{\fnArial\fs18}How can you talk to me about Quinn?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.34,0:09:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,她才不会遇到这样的问题\N{\fnArial\fs18}She'll never have this kind of problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.34,0:09:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,思考一类的问题\N{\fnArial\fs18}It involves thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.87,0:09:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,是你让我倾吐有什么烦恼 还一个劲儿接电话\N{\fnArial\fs18}You make me tell you what's wrong, in between calls,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.85,0:09:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,结果就是拿Quinn举例?\N{\fnArial\fs18}and then you bring up Quinn?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.25,0:09:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底了不了解我啊?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Don't you know me at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.66,0:09:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,有你的 Morgendorffer\N{\fnArial\fs18}Good one, Morgendorffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.93,0:09:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,尼玛\N{\fnArial\fs18}Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.86,0:09:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊 什么都不做就这么懒着简直爽死了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Man, what a good day to just kick back and chill.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.53,0:09:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,说得一点不错\N{\fnArial\fs18}You got that right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.49,0:09:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,没空说话哟\N{\fnArial\fs18}Can't stop to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.61,0:09:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,四小时后去Stacy家参加盛大派对 该打扮咯\N{\fnArial\fs18}A big party at Stacy's in four hours. Gotta dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.63,0:09:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Quinn 你不觉得自己把社交这种事情看太重了吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Quinn, don't you think you've taken this popularity thing too far?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.20,0:09:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,说你们一天到晚瞎玩\N{\fnArial\fs18}This well-liked teen crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.74,0:09:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,就不能有点深度啥的吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Don't you have any depth at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.06,0:09:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么就不能跟Daira多学学?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Why can't you be more like Daria?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.39,0:09:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 Daria\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, hey, Daria.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.47,0:09:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你们需要单独和Quinn谈一下吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Um, do you want to talk to Quinn alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.37,0:09:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不用 宝贝儿 其实呢\N{\fnArial\fs18}No, sweetie. As a matter of fact,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.68,0:09:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在跟她说 希望她能多跟你学学呢\N{\fnArial\fs18}we were just telling her how we wish she'd be more like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.91,0:09:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不止一次了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.93,0:09:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,其实不是每个人都拥有...\N{\fnArial\fs18}Well, not everyone can have the same...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:10:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你们以为我不想像Daria一样嘛?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Don't you think I want to be more like Daria?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.76,0:10:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,如果可以 我有怎么不想像她呢?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Don't you think I would if I could?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.73,0:10:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊 爸爸妈妈 你们怎么就搞不懂呢?\N{\fnArial\fs18}God, Mom and Dad, why won't you accept it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.30,0:10:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我永远成不了Daria\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'll never be like Daria.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.42,0:10:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的诅咒 也是我的负累\N{\fnArial\fs18}That's my curse... and my burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.14,0:10:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道这不怪你们\N{\fnArial\fs18}I know it's not your fault,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.15,0:10:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,可看看你们又遗传了多少完美基因?\N{\fnArial\fs18}but look what your perfection has done to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.20,0:10:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不要去安慰一下她什么的吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Shouldn't we comfort her or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.10,0:10:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,让她哭去吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, let her go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.74,0:10:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,会没事的\N{\fnArial\fs18}She'll get over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.05,0:10:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那至少也应该告诉她\N{\fnArial\fs18}We should at least tell her about
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.46,0:10:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,屋外的八道高速路晚上在施工吧?\N{\fnArial\fs18}that eight-lane highway they built outside the house during the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.46,0:10:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你这么说也对\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hmm... you may be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.72,0:10:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不是什么好事\N{\fnArial\fs18}That can't be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.80,0:10:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐\N{\fnArial\fs18}Ow! God!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.13,0:10:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,又一大作\N{\fnArial\fs18}Another masterpiece.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.29,0:10:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,如此看来 我这前半生都活在一场骗局里\N{\fnArial\fs18}So it turns out that my life up to now has been a sham.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.19,0:10:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我根本不会写东西 连简单的故事都编不出\N{\fnArial\fs18}I can't write. I can't produce a simple story.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.12,0:10:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 Daira 打死我也想不到你会缺少想象力呀\N{\fnArial\fs18}Wow, Daria. I never figured you for a lack of imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.53,0:10:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我有想象力\N{\fnArial\fs18}I have imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.17,0:11:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以想出各种点子 但没一个能让人感到真实\N{\fnArial\fs18}I can come up with all sorts of ideas, but none of them feels true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.90,0:11:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那你对"真实"的定义是?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Well, what's your definition of "true"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.03,0:11:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,能讲出一些东西的东西\N{\fnArial\fs18}Something that says something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.81,0:11:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么? 什么东西都行吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}What? Anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.13,0:11:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不 意义 讲出意义的东西\N{\fnArial\fs18}No, something. About something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.50,0:11:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我来整理下思路\N{\fnArial\fs18}Let me get this straight:
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.47,0:11:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你是跟我说 你想写出点东西来\N{\fnArial\fs18}you're telling me you want to write something,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.98,0:11:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,但不是什么东西都行 而是能讲出点东西的东西\N{\fnArial\fs18}not just anything, that says something about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.56,0:11:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fnArial\fs18}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.02,0:11:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,说你有沟通障碍 谁会信啊\N{\fnArial\fs18}Who'd ever believe you're having trouble communicating.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.37,0:11:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,敲门的这位 我叫你什么?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Whom shall I say is calling?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.00,0:11:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria 你有什么事想要说出来的吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Daria, is there anything you want to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.36,0:11:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,没 谢谢过问\N{\fnArial\fs18}No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.51,0:11:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,确定吗 亲爱的?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Are you sure, sweetie?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.25,0:11:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要自己静一静 让情绪平稳下来\N{\fnArial\fs18}I need some time alone to work out my feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.87,0:11:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria\N{\fnArial\fs18}Daria!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.77,0:11:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,或者玩填字游戏\N{\fnArial\fs18}Or do a crossword.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.35,0:11:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria...\N{\fnArial\fs18}Daria...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.41,0:11:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Helen 我的炖菜 炉子着火了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Gah, Helen! My stew... the stove's on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.17,0:11:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,看在上帝份上...\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, for the love of...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.13,0:11:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,邪恶之母 撒旦之妹 告诉我你在这污秽的炖菜中看到了什么?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Unholy mother, sister of Satan, tell me what you see in your filthy brew.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.30,0:12:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,拨开时间的迷雾 说说我未来何在?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Say what the mists of time hold for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.54,0:12:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你付过款了吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Have you my payment?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.28,0:12:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我要新生儿的嫩嫩小肝脏\N{\fnArial\fs18}The tender liver of a newborn babe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.64,0:12:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我... 来得有点急 你接受支票吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}I, um, was in a rush. Will you take a check?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.23,0:12:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,支票?! 你不会拿假身份证号哄我吧?\N{\fnArial\fs18}A check?! Have you two forms of I.D.?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.30,0:12:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我你将赐予我力量\N{\fnArial\fs18}Tell me you can bring me power!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.37,0:12:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,护佑我杀敌无数 凯旋而归\N{\fnArial\fs18}Power to crush my enemies, to triumph over all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.69,0:12:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以赐予此等力量\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yes, I can bring you this power.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.39,0:12:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,但凭什么好工作都得让男人拿下?\N{\fnArial\fs18}But why should men get all the good jobs?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.65,0:12:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我你可以赐予我力量\N{\fnArial\fs18}Tell me you can bring me power!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.37,0:12:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,护佑我杀敌无数 凯旋而归\N{\fnArial\fs18}Power to crush my enemies, to triumph over all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.25,0:12:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,真是等不及尝尝这炖菜了\N{\fnArial\fs18}I can't wait to taste this stew!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.76,0:12:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,否则我以生养你的罪恶魔鬼之名发誓 我将统治这片大地\N{\fnArial\fs18}Or I swear by the unholy imp that spawned you, I will rule the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.65,0:12:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那我还统治什么啊?\N{\fnArial\fs18}But what do I get to rule?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.21,0:12:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴 没牙老巫婆\N{\fnArial\fs18}Silence, toothless hag!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.79,0:12:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,干嘛对人家人身攻击\N{\fnArial\fs18}You don't have to get personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.25,0:12:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria 独家课业任务完成怎么样了?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Daria! How's the special assignment going?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.82,0:12:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我找您来就为这事儿\N{\fnArial\fs18}Um, that's what I want to talk to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.69,0:13:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想做了\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'd like not to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.10,0:13:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不要嘛 怎么了呢 Daria\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, no. What's the matter, Daria?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.26,0:13:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么也写不出来吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}You haven't been able to write anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.09,0:13:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不是 我写了好多出来 可没有一个能拿得出手\N{\fnArial\fs18}No, I've written a lot of stuff, but it's not up to my standards.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.53,0:13:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我有点烦 因为我也不知道什么叫拿得出手\N{\fnArial\fs18}And that disturbs me, because I don't have standards.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.26,0:13:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么呢?\N{\fnArial\fs18}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.28,0:13:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,都是因为要拿身边的人做角色来源\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's this idea of using people I know as characters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.38,0:13:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得还是完全虚构出来一拨人比较好办\N{\fnArial\fs18}I think I might be better off with a bunch of characters I just made up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.45,0:13:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,可这正是科幻小说挑战人的地方呀 Daria\N{\fnArial\fs18}But that's the challenge of the fiction writer, Daria.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.37,0:13:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,将现实生活中的所见所感融会贯通 再注入到非现实之中\N{\fnArial\fs18}To take what we learn in real life and turn it into something that's not really real,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.58,0:13:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,其自身又构成了某种意义上的现实\N{\fnArial\fs18}but has a real life all its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.88,0:13:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 理论上听起来很赞 应该是吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}Well, that sounds great in theory... I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.24,0:13:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不过我想不出我的那些角色应该做些什么\N{\fnArial\fs18}But I can't figure out what my characters should be doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.76,0:13:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,没事 这很好办\N{\fnArial\fs18}Okay. That's not a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.75,0:13:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我们微调一下作业的要求\N{\fnArial\fs18}We'll alter the assignment slightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.54,0:13:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,有些时候界限反而能给我们带来自由\N{\fnArial\fs18}Sometimes boundaries can paradoxically provide us with freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.79,0:13:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就来写一写活动相关的东西吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}We'll say it should include an activity of some kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.39,0:13:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,想想哈 森林篝火吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Let's see... a forest fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.26,0:13:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 那可能就成了悲剧了\N{\fnArial\fs18}No, that could end in tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.17,0:13:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,要不写写去检查视力?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Some kind of orthoscopic surgery?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.02,0:13:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 那太凌乱了\N{\fnArial\fs18}No, that can get messy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.72,0:13:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,有了 写纸牌游戏\N{\fnArial\fs18}I know, a game of cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.63,0:13:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,纸牌游戏?\N{\fnArial\fs18}A game of cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.86,0:14:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,对啊 随便写什么样的纸牌游戏都可以\N{\fnArial\fs18}Sure, and it can be any card game you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.92,0:14:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,天 谢了 真是太有帮助了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Gee, thanks. That'll really help.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.27,0:14:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,很高兴你这么说 加油\N{\fnArial\fs18}Glad to hear it. Have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.27,0:14:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,罪恶之母 撒旦之妹 告诉我你在这污秽的炖菜中看到了什么?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Unholy mother, sister of Satan, tell me what you see in your filthy brew.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.12,0:14:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,拨开时间的迷雾 说说我未来何在?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Tell me what the mists of time hold for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.39,0:14:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你付过款了吗? 我要新生儿的嫩嫩小肝脏\N{\fnArial\fs18}Have you my payment? The tender liver of a newborn babe?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.16,0:14:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我肝脏有点缺货\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'm a little short on livers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.15,0:14:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这样吧 跟你玩一个五张抽牌小魔术怎么样?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Tell you what: play you a quick game of five-card stud for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.89,0:14:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,选J没得跑\N{\fnArial\fs18}Jacks are wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.17,0:14:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria? Daria 电视没开\N{\fnArial\fs18}Daria? Daria, the TV's not on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.04,0:14:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,嘘 我在看呢\N{\fnArial\fs18}Shh! I'm watching this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.78,0:14:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria 妈妈很抱歉之前没有太照顾你的感受\N{\fnArial\fs18}Daria, I'm sorry about not being more sensitive earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.36,0:14:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,确定没因为拿两个闺女互相比较...\N{\fnArial\fs18}Doesn't comparing one sibling to another
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.62,0:14:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,在教子入门课上得不及格嘛?\N{\fnArial\fs18}get you an automatic "F" in Parenting 101?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.29,0:14:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,世上没有教子入门课\N{\fnArial\fs18}There is no Parenting 101.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.67,0:14:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这也是问题所在\N{\fnArial\fs18}That's the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.12,0:14:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,没有哪门课能教会你怎么做一个完美的家长\N{\fnArial\fs18}There's no course that can teach you to be a perfect mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.40,0:14:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,显而易见\N{\fnArial\fs18}That's obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.72,0:15:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria 妈妈为之前没能帮到你道歉\N{\fnArial\fs18}Daria, I apologized for not helping you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.03,0:15:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在来帮助你了\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'm offering to help you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.98,0:15:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在要做什么?\N{\fnArial\fs18}What do you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.71,0:15:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我的故事烂透了\N{\fnArial\fs18}My story sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.43,0:15:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的 我相信只要再多给你一天或者两天...\N{\fnArial\fs18}Well, honey, I'm sure if you just give it another day or two...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.16,0:15:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我能做的都已经做了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Everything I do has already been done.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.25,0:15:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我想写点有意义的东西出来\N{\fnArial\fs18}I wanted to write something meaningful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.22,0:15:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,可我什么也写不出来\N{\fnArial\fs18}I can't write anything at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.71,0:15:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,也许你有点过度在意了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Maybe you're trying too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.62,0:15:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,没必要写出什么有意义的东西 只要写出真实的东西就好了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Maybe you don't have to write something meaningful, just something honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.45,0:15:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,真实的东西我可以\N{\fnArial\fs18}I can do honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.64,0:15:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,看看周围 描述我看到的东西就好了\N{\fnArial\fs18}I look around me, I describe what I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.11,0:15:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不如写点你想要看到的场景咯 如实来写\N{\fnArial\fs18}How about describing what you'd like to see, honestly?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.98,0:15:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这话什么意思?\N{\fnArial\fs18}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.91,0:15:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria 世上最简单的事莫过于...\N{\fnArial\fs18}Daria, the easiest thing in the world for you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.24,0:15:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,如实看待眼前的一切\N{\fnArial\fs18}is being honest about what you observe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.09,0:15:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,所以...\N{\fnArial\fs18}And...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.86,0:15:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,难的在于 如实面对内心里的渴望\N{\fnArial\fs18}What's hard for you is being honest about your wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.03,0:15:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得事情该是什么样子 如果不该是现在这样的话\N{\fnArial\fs18}About the way you think things should be, not the way they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.27,0:15:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你用愤世嫉俗的吐槽遮掩着内心的渴望\N{\fnArial\fs18}You gloss over it with a cynical joke
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.80,0:15:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,没人知道你真正信仰什么\N{\fnArial\fs18}and nobody finds out what you really believe in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.85,0:15:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,看来我的邪恶计划奏效了\N{\fnArial\fs18}So my evil plan is working.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.53,0:15:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想要真实的东西 就要诚心说出自己希望事情什么样\N{\fnArial\fs18}If you really want to be honest, be truthful about what you'd like to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.94,0:15:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这可是挑战所在\N{\fnArial\fs18}There's a challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.77,0:15:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么时候这么了解我的?\N{\fnArial\fs18}When the hell did you learn so much about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.94,0:16:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这事很有趣的 Daria\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's a funny thing, Daria.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.71,0:16:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,对于给予了她生命的人 你会不自觉想密切监视她\N{\fnArial\fs18}You give birth to someone, you just get an urge to keep tabs on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.81,0:16:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 亲爱的\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, hi, sweetie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.13,0:16:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,还好吗 老妈?\N{\fnArial\fs18}How are you, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.33,0:16:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,很不错 就是每天早晨从床上爬起来要稍微费一点劲\N{\fnArial\fs18}Pretty good. You know, every morning it's a little harder to get out of bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.96,0:16:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是\N{\fnArial\fs18}For me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.90,0:16:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你老爸就不一样了 好像一天比一天年轻似的\N{\fnArial\fs18}Your father, on the other hand, seems to be getting younger every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.78,0:16:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,自从退休 他这人生才算是开启了新篇章\N{\fnArial\fs18}Ever since he retired he's developed such a wonderful perspective.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.94,0:16:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,男人做过心脏搭桥手术是会这样的\N{\fnArial\fs18}Well, triple bypass surgery will do that for a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.71,0:16:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Marcello怎么样了?\N{\fnArial\fs18}How's Marcello?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.35,0:16:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,还在和其他教工奋争课程表上的课时呢\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, fighting the same old curriculum battles against the rest of the faculty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.26,0:16:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs26\an8}帮助宝宝学会控制大小便的训练
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.26,0:16:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,另外每年秋天都是新生的如厕训练季\N{\fnArial\fs18}And each fall there's a new batch of freshmen to potty-train.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.86,0:16:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你这种的专栏写的不错\N{\fnArial\fs18}I enjoyed your column this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.28,0:16:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我们本打算和脱教者布道\N{\fnArial\fs18}We're preaching to the converted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.90,0:16:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我义愤填膺 读者也义愤填膺 结果就是没有结果\N{\fnArial\fs18}I get outraged, the readers get outraged, and nothing happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.36,0:16:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,有时我都觉得自己应该转战电视台\N{\fnArial\fs18}Sometimes I think I should have gone into television.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.38,0:16:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你上电视 Daria?\N{\fnArial\fs18}You in television, Daria?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.17,0:16:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 我还是别扯了\N{\fnArial\fs18}I know. Who am I kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.12,0:16:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你们俩有没有好好谈谈要小孩的事情啊?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Has there been any further discussion about expanding your little family?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.63,0:16:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,妈... 你知道我还没准备好要宝宝\N{\fnArial\fs18}Mom... you know I'm not ready for kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.06,0:17:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,一想到要小孩我就很不安 也不知道是为什么\N{\fnArial\fs18}The whole idea makes me uneasy and I'm not sure why.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.82,0:17:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,给我\N{\fnArial\fs18}Give me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.57,0:17:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不给 我的\N{\fnArial\fs18}No, it's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.13,0:17:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,妈咪\N{\fnArial\fs18}Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.59,0:17:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,想起来了 所以我不想要小孩\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, yeah. Now I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.47,0:17:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 你们知道奶奶家的电视在哪\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hi. You know where Grandma's TV is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.96,0:17:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,去找乖节目看去吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}Go watch something educational.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.98,0:17:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐 累死我了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Boy, I'm exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.55,0:17:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,面向少女的隆胸手术...\N{\fnArial\fs18}Breast implants for chickens...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.89,0:17:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这个不行\N{\fnArial\fs18}Not that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.53,0:17:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,还好吗 Quinn?\N{\fnArial\fs18}How are you, Quinn?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.86,0:17:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,您知道的 日复一日 孩子复孩子\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, you know, another day, another baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.98,0:17:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我发誓 趁哪天Jamie不注意\N{\fnArial\fs18}I swear, one of these days I'm going to slip something into Jamie's beer
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我非得往他酒里放点什么 然后出去做结扎手术\N{\fnArial\fs18}and while he's unconscious, I'm going to go out and get my tubes tied.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.96,0:17:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,更高明的是让他做\N{\fnArial\fs18}Better yet, his tubes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.19,0:17:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,老爸怎么样? 叫我们来有事?\N{\fnArial\fs18}How's Dad? And what's he want?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.43,0:17:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我挺好 咕咕\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'm great. Goo-goo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.95,0:17:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 那啥 姑娘们 爸想修改一下遗嘱...\N{\fnArial\fs18}Sorry. You know, girls, I was going over my will...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.35,0:17:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,又来啊\N{\fnArial\fs18}Not again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.33,0:17:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,老爸 您干嘛这么心重啊?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Daddy, why are you so morbid?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.45,0:17:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这话我也问过他\N{\fnArial\fs18}That's exactly what I asked him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.54,0:17:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,可我就是想改一下遗嘱\N{\fnArial\fs18}But I like going over my will.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.97,0:17:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,满满都是钞票呀\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's got all that money!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.46,0:17:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,老爸 两周前你才刚刚修改过\N{\fnArial\fs18}Dad, you revised your will two weeks ago
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.97,0:17:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你在阁楼上发现你以前的废纸编织环了\N{\fnArial\fs18}when you discovered your old gum wrapper chain in the attic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.71,0:17:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子们肯定会喜欢的\N{\fnArial\fs18}The kids are going to love that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.37,0:18:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 大伙来谈谈我改遗嘱的事儿吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}Anyway, who said anything about revising my will?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.01,0:18:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那 这次又要怎么改?\N{\fnArial\fs18}So, what are we doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.71,0:18:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我读了自己的遗嘱 回顾过去 遥想未来\N{\fnArial\fs18}Well, I was reading my will, thinking about the past and the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.47,0:18:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,忽然就想到 你们俩姑娘都变成了爸爸希望的样子\N{\fnArial\fs18}and it occurred to me that you girls have turned out exactly the way I hoped.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.21,0:18:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好了啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.06,0:18:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria 每周你都会有自己的专栏\N{\fnArial\fs18}Daria, every week you write that column of yours,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.35,0:18:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,努力唤醒人们接近真相\N{\fnArial\fs18}trying to wake people up to the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.52,0:18:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我闺女可是个改革者\N{\fnArial\fs18}My daughter, the crusader.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.61,0:18:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 说着同样的话 高中时被看成异己...\N{\fnArial\fs18}Well, there is some pleasure in winning awards
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.47,0:18:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,现在却凭它拿了大奖 感觉也还不错\N{\fnArial\fs18}for saying the same things that made me an outcast in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.48,0:18:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,再说Quinn...\N{\fnArial\fs18}And Quinn,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.02,0:18:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你把过去一个劲儿要变得... 稍微有那么点自以为是的劲头\N{\fnArial\fs18}you've taken all that energy and enthusiasm you used to direct toward being,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.96,0:18:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,把那股劲头和热情...\N{\fnArial\fs18}um, a teensy bit self-absorbed...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.08,0:18:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,老爸 我那时是不知天高地厚的小恶魔\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, daddy, I was a stuck-up little nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.54,0:18:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,全都倾注到养育孩子们身上了\N{\fnArial\fs18}...and put it all into bringing up those kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.68,0:18:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这可不是轻松活儿 相信妈 妈懂的\N{\fnArial\fs18}And that's no easy task. Believe me, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.72,0:18:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么从来没听你抱怨过你们家这几个小淘气鬼 Quinn?\N{\fnArial\fs18}How come you never complain about those little monsters of yours, Quinn?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.05,0:18:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱他们呀 爸\N{\fnArial\fs18}Um, I like them, Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.28,0:18:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我还是搞不懂今天到底要干嘛\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'm still not clear on what all this is about.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.79,0:18:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,老爸想起了许多过去的事情 然后我就想 嘿\N{\fnArial\fs18}Well, I was having so much fun reminiscing I thought, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.46,0:19:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,咱干嘛不像过去一样 一家人一起玩玩家庭卡片游戏?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Why don't we get together for a family card game just like we used to?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.54,0:19:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,家庭卡片游戏?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Family card game?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.07,0:19:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就从来都没玩过家庭卡片游戏的好不?\N{\fnArial\fs18}We never played a family card game in our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.75,0:19:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria说的对\N{\fnArial\fs18}Daria's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.11,0:19:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我又听到了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, do I hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.63,0:19:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得叫我爸爸一起去"钓鱼"\N{\fnArial\fs18}I remember asking my father to play "go fish"...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.20,0:19:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,小心搭桥啊 爸\N{\fnArial\fs18}Triple bypass, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.42,0:19:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好 我没事\N{\fnArial\fs18}Okay, I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.42,0:19:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那好吧 去他的 我们压根就没玩过家庭卡片游戏\N{\fnArial\fs18}Anyway, so screw it, then, we never played a family card game.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.33,0:19:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们现在玩咯\N{\fnArial\fs18}Let's play one now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.96,0:19:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- 桥? - 松子酒\N{\fnArial\fs18}- Bridge? - Gin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.97,0:19:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- 桃心 - 好嘞\N{\fnArial\fs18}- Hearts. - Done.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.42,0:19:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,成啦 我要玩桃心游戏\N{\fnArial\fs18}Okay. I'm going to play a game of hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.60,0:19:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我漂亮的老伴儿和两个棒棒的闺女\N{\fnArial\fs18}with my beautiful wife and my two great kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.99,0:19:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Jake\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, Jake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.03,0:19:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样 Daria? 选桃心?\N{\fnArial\fs18}How about it, Daria? Hearts?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.90,0:19:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,算我咯\N{\fnArial\fs18}Deal me in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.67,0:19:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不太好 对吧?\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's not very good, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.19,0:19:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria...\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, Daria...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.49,0:19:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,也没那么糟吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}It wasn't that bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.18,0:19:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,干嘛 干嘛 故事而已 不是真的\N{\fnArial\fs18}Stop, stop! This isn't a story, it's real life!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.57,0:19:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你写的故事把你妈给看哭了?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Wow, so your story made your mother cry?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.75,0:19:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,喜极而泣 这是烦人的地方\N{\fnArial\fs18}Out of happiness. That's the sick part.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.82,0:19:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,再说说她为啥哭来着?\N{\fnArial\fs18}And run the reason by me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.42,0:20:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,她觉得这事儿说明 我私底下其实没有看上去的那么隔路\N{\fnArial\fs18}She took it as evidence that I'm secretly not as alienated as I seem or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.80,0:20:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,得花好多年才能消除这误解了\N{\fnArial\fs18}It'll take me years to undo the damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.35,0:20:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,要拿给O'Neill老师看嘛?\N{\fnArial\fs18}So you going to show it to O'Neill?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.48,0:20:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,别无选择\N{\fnArial\fs18}I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.67,0:20:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,但要是他也哭 我就打算退学了\N{\fnArial\fs18}But if he cries, too, I'm dropping out of school.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.18,0:20:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 反正你现在态度也端正了 啥都挺好\N{\fnArial\fs18}Well, listen, now that you've got such a great attitude and everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.93,0:20:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,能把靴子送我吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}can I have your boots?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.15,0:20:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,行啊 转过去 我现在就送你一脚\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yeah. Turn around and I'll give you one right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.45,0:20:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria 你看... 哪天...\N{\fnArial\fs18}Daria, do you think... someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.20,0:20:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我能读读你的故事吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}I can read your story?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.11,0:20:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 不过你可以读读你和Kevin私奔的那个\N{\fnArial\fs18}No. But you can read the one where you run away with Kevin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.68,0:20:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,啥?!\N{\fnArial\fs18}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.02,0:20:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs25\fn方正准圆简体\fsp1\c&HE6ECE8&\pos(414,147)}欢迎微博关注\N\N{\fs32}@漫迪字幕组
